    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Ishimaru Clan are some of the finest practitioners of Ninjutsu and Taijutsu of the Hidden Stone. Some of its more talented members form an entire squad of the Tsuchikage&#x27;s elite guard . Their combat style is as simplistic as it is brutal.</p><p><b>Source:</b> Mechanics/Character_Options/Occupations/Ishimaru Clan.md</p><p><b>Category:</b> Core</p><p><b>Prerequisite:</b> Age 8+</p><p><b>Class Skills:</b> Select 2 from Climb, Hide, Jump, Ninjutsu, Survival, Taijutsu.</p><p><b>Feat:</b> Select one from Advanced Bloodline (Fortify), Archaic Weapon Proficiency, Armor Proficiency (light, medium), Brawl, Combat Martial Arts, Defensive Martial Arts, Genin, Nin Weapons Proficiency, Ninjutsu Adept, Taijutsu Adept.</p><p><b>Wealth Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p><p><b>Reputation Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p><p><b>Affiliation:</b> You require 1 less success to learn Ishimaru Hujutsu techniques.</p>"
